TEXT.S: = Masitoban = Gaga mniq Nantowseyn Jnaysyang ka alang Masitoban. 188 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 450 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 94% niqan 422 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 6% niqan 28 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Tayal90%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq1%, Bunun1%, Amis1%.
